ComicInfo.Summary:
The new arc of the hit Wonderland series begins! Where do you go when there is nowhere left to run? Back to the beginning! Tired of fleeing from Wonderland, Calie and Violet begin to search for answers by delving into Charles Dodsgon's past. But a mysterious force from Wonderland might have other, darker plans in mind for them.
Notes:
Cover B is a homage of Leonardo da Vinci's Mona Lisa painting.
